M||tx|---
M||titl|Don't Define cp Inside cp
M||impa|hi
M||impa|prevents remount on every render
M||tags|rerender, cp, remount, perf
M||tx|---
M|Don'|**Im|hi (prevents remount on every render)**
M|Don'|tx|Defining a cp inside another cp creates a new cp tp on every render. rc sees a different cp each time and fully remounts it, destroying all state and DOM.
M|Don'|tx|A common reason developers do this is to access parent variables w/o passing props. Always pass props instead.
M|Don'|**In|**
M|Don'|tx|```tsx
M|Don'|tx|fn UserProfile({ us, theme }) {
M|Don'|tx|// Defined inside to access `theme` - BAD
M|Don'|tx|const Avatar = () => (
M|Don'|tx|<img
M|Don'|tx|src={us.avatarUrl}
M|Don'|clas|'avatar-light'}
M|Don'|tx|/>
M|Don'|tx|)
M|Don'|tx|// Defined inside to access `us` - BAD
M|Don'|tx|const Stats = () => (
M|Don'|tx|<div>
M|Don'|tx|<span>{us.followers} followers</span>
M|Don'|tx|<span>{us.posts} posts</span>
M|Don'|tx|</div>
M|Don'|tx|)
M|Don'|tx|return (
M|Don'|tx|<div>
M|Don'|tx|<Avatar />
M|Don'|tx|<Stats />
M|Don'|tx|</div>
M|Don'|tx|)
M|Don'|tx|}
M|Don'|tx|```
M|Don'|tx|Every time `UserProfile` renders, `Avatar` and `Stats` are new cp tp. rc unmounts the old instances and mounts new ones, losing any internal state, running effects again, and recreating DOM nodes.
M|Don'|**Co|**
M|Don'|tx|```tsx
M|Don'|func|{ src: string; theme: string }) {
M|Don'|tx|return (
M|Don'|tx|<img
M|Don'|tx|src={src}
M|Don'|clas|'avatar-light'}
M|Don'|tx|/>
M|Don'|tx|)
M|Don'|tx|}
M|Don'|func|{ followers: number; posts: number }) {
M|Don'|tx|return (
M|Don'|tx|<div>
M|Don'|tx|<span>{followers} followers</span>
M|Don'|tx|<span>{posts} posts</span>
M|Don'|tx|</div>
M|Don'|tx|)
M|Don'|tx|}
M|Don'|tx|fn UserProfile({ us, theme }) {
M|Don'|tx|return (
M|Don'|tx|<div>
M|Don'|tx|<Avatar src={us.avatarUrl} theme={theme} />
M|Don'|tx|<Stats followers={us.followers} posts={us.posts} />
M|Don'|tx|</div>
M|Don'|tx|)
M|Don'|tx|}
M|Don'|tx|```
M|Don'|**Sy|**
M|Don'|it|Input fields lose focus on every keystroke
M|Don'|it|Animations restart unexpectedly
M|Don'|it|`useEffect` cleanup/setup runs on every parent render
M|Don'|it|Scroll position resets inside the cp